  "title": "Intern, Fundraising & Partnerships",
  "description": "<p>Key Responsibilities:</p><p>1. Reception & Donor Services</p><ul><li>Answer incoming phone calls related to zakat, donations, and general enquiries</li><li>Manage and respond to WhatsApp donor enquiries in a timely and professional manner</li><li>Attend to walk-in donors during operating hours on weekdays and Saturday mornings</li><li>Handle donor enquiries received via email, escalating complex matters when required</li></ul><p>2. Donation Processing & Administrative Support</p><ul><li>Receive and record donations received via mail and walk-ins, including cash and cheque</li><li>Support the processing of all donations received, ensuring accurate documentation and proper handover</li><li>Print zakat receipts and prepare them for mailing to donors</li><li>Support basic administrative tasks related to donor records and donor correspondence</li><li>Ensure proper handling of donor-related documents in accordance with internal procedures</li></ul><p>3. Fundraising Campaign Support (Throughout Internship)</p><ul><li>Provide administrative and on-ground support for fundraising campaigns, as required</li><li>Support fundraising marketing activities, including drafting or updating emails and WhatsApp messages, assisting with the updating of campaign collaterals and materials and support ad-hoc campaign-related tasks during peak fundraising periods</li></ul><p>4. General Administrative & Cross-Departmental Support</p><ul><li>Provide administrative support for organisational projects beyond fundraising, where required</li><li>Assist with preparations for organisation-wide events, including year-end initiatives</li><li>Assist with other ad-hoc administrative duties assigned by the supervisor</li></ul>",
